{"tid":2393107,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"後悔1年前從武漢登上英國航機 英國男子：留在武漢更安全及自由","createTime":"2021-02-03T08:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T09:02:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e605247c8a866438f4aaef553a56d1aed1fe5725","tid":2393107,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情已持續逾一年，英國去年派出專機由武漢接載國民回到英國。根據《BBC》報道，有乘搭專機返回英國的男子表示後悔，認為自己當初應該留在武漢。他指，若當初留在武漢，會更為安全及自由，更稱被英國政府欺騙，因返回英國後並沒有更安全。<br />\n<br />\n去年武漢曾進入封城狀態，39歲的韋拉（Matt Raw）表示，當接收到英國政府 「離開武漢」的指示時，但最初英國政府只允許英國公民登上專機，韋拉不願和中國籍的妻子分開，所以並未打算搭乘航班。<br />\n<br />\n但最後英國政府宣佈，英國公民的伴侶，即使只持有中國護照亦可登機。韋拉夫婦匆忙收拾行李後，便趕往機場。<br />\n<br />\n最後韋拉夫婦、韋拉媽媽和其他一共83名人士，於去年1月31日乘坐專機離開武漢。並於抵達後接受了兩個禮拜的隔離。<br />\n<br />\n現在，韋拉說他寧願自己「沒有登上撤僑包機」，他認為自己被英國政府騙了，「他們說謊，我們被告知離開武漢，回到英國，英國是安全的。」但韋拉認為，如果他們留在中國，會比目前留在英國更安全，更自由。<br />\n<br />\n韋拉認同中國政府迅速地封鎖了整個城市，是正確的做法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2870002/UK_thumb_20210203_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2870002%2FUK_thumb_20210203_J_1024.jpg&h=96088e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e4fc0bef250e93511f013402c2539efd1a33d05","tid":2393107,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"可以做支那鬼<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/fine-02142020071752.html/021420-cn-fine.png/@@images/cc0fab22-a0ed-4109-8561-aecb18f324df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Ffine-02142020071752.html%2F021420-cn-fine.png%2F%40%40images%2Fcc0fab22-a0ed-4109-8561-aecb18f324df.png&h=f91abfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1052c520dd319c390a5b87d19bad499d3115c96","tid":2393107,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"更加證明到呢隻病毒係支那製造出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff266f637e92c7e2cfd6b0ceaea66ab152070c3","tid":2393107,"uid":194130,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"佢未返到英國果時英國係安全既<br />\n就係佢由武漢帶病毒飛去英國<br />\n英國就唔安全啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b884d76661aa768f21a3d74b3890e89ee63cd48","tid":2393107,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"又一個BNO post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6669e71a6704045c21a911584a31a12789e25b0e","tid":2393107,"uid":213446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"咁叫佢番支共啦<br />\n唔好留起大英帝國啦 好危險架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49ecad8e4553f7cef9c20d20e09305af1907b4e","tid":2393107,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣真係仆街黎<br />\n<br />\nBut he says he now wishes he had &quot;never got on that flight&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;They lied to us,&quot; he says of the UK authorities. &quot;We're being told to get out of Wuhan, 'come back to England, you'll be safe here'.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We would have been safer and much more freer if we stayed in China.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-manchester-55830497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-manchester-55830497&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjX%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=90d6c8ff\" data-ef-url=